title: Bright & spacious Spring home close to The Woodlands Mall
posting_body: ['If you love to entertain, this classic 4 bed, 2 bath Spring home is perfect for you!', 'The large living room features lots of room to relax and socialize.', 'Plus, there’s a bonus space that makes a fantastic game room or home office.', 'Other highlights include new wood-look flooring, an elegant foyer, a separate dining room, stainless steel appliances, and updated light fixtures and ceiling fans.', 'Best of all, large windows let in great natural light.', 'The primary bedroom suite offers double closets, a spa-style tub, and a separate shower.', 'The full-size washer/dryer set here will make laundry day a breeze.', 'Additional convenience amenities include air conditioning and a dishwasher in the light and updated kitchen.', 'This peaceful Spring neighborhood features tree-lined streets and a pleasant suburban feel only 23 miles north of Houston.', 'The Woodlands Mall is a short 15-minute drive from home, and you’ll also be close to I-45 and 99 when you need to get around the area.', 'There’s a Target nearby, and plenty of grocery stores, including H-E-B, ALDI, Kroger, and Sprouts Farmers Market.', 'Bridgestone Neighborhood Park, Ponderosa Walking Park, and other green spaces are also minutes away.', 'Dining and drinking spots near home include The Greasy Spoon, Chuan, Fu Manchung, Tapped Drafthouse & Kitchen, and Q-Shi BBQ & Sushi.']
